Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.79,0:01:29.06,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Let's come together
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.20,0:01:33.35,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Can't seem to stop my imagination
