Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.18,0:01:40.46,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Another matter
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.56,0:01:45.89,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}But I can't deny，I'm faced with a tricky temptation
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.93,0:01:51.30,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}In the world that keeps on changing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.40,0:01:56.56,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Don't know why my heart is aching
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.75,0:02:05.71,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Gotta handle it，no more hesitation
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.90,0:02:08.72,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}There can be no turning back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.75,0:02:09.88,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}God only knows
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.93,0:02:12.59,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}“My mind is as free as the wind
