Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.07,0:02:17.14,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}God only knows
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:20.08,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}“I don't need that kind of real things
