Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.52,0:02:24.58,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}God only knows
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.70,0:02:27.43,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}“There must be the meaning of life
