Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.85,0:02:32.00,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}God only knows
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.05,0:02:34.78,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}“Just believe in myself and my dream
